{"word":"θηρευτής","slug":"θηρευτής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>θηρευτής</b></el> <el>(θηρευτής, οῦ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:θηρεύω'><el>θηρεύω</el></a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:θηρατής'><el>θηρατής</el></a>,\n<p/><i>a hunter, huntsman</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <el>κυσὶ θηρευτῇσι</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; also of <i>a fisher</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/>"}]}